rom\": 1036, \"to\": 1055}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's hard work.\", \"from\": 1084, \"to\": 1102, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hard work\", \"from\": 1092, \"to\": 1101}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He's obviously pretty dominant in the 5,000.\", \"from\": 1104, \"to\": 1149, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We will see.\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1162, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I can not see him running the 1,500 for a whole another Olympic cycle but he's running really fast times so that's not for me to determine.\", \"from\": 1163, \"to\": 1302, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a whole\", \"from\": 1203, \"to\": 1210}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will be sticking to the 1,500m.\\\"\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1337, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 1,500m.\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1336}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kerr and Ingebrigtsen had exchanged constant barbs since the Briton edged out his rival in the World Championships final in Budapest last year.\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1482, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1463, \"end\": 1471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.9997001084299435, \"rank\": 0.00029998146184316386, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kerr\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1343}, {\"ngram\": \"Ingebrigtsen\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1360}, {\"ngram\": \"constant barbs\", \"from\": 1375, \"to\": 1389}, {\"ngram\": \"the Briton\", \"from\": 1396, \"to\": 1406}, {\"ngram\": \"his rival\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1426}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Championships\", \"from\": 1430, \"to\": 1453}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kerr accused him of lacking manners and said he had a number of weaknesses, while Ingebrigtsen hit back suggesting Kerr never turned up to races outsid