o\": 2053}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Today, Cole Hocker, Yared Nuguse and Josh Kerr outsmarted me.\", \"from\": 2057, \"to\": 2119, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2065, \"end\": 2076, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cole_Hocker\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cole Hocker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cole_Hocker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cole_Hocker\"}, {\"begin\": 2078, \"end\": 2090, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yared_Nuguse\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yared Nuguse\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yared_Nuguse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yared_Nuguse\"}, {\"begin\": 2095, \"end\": 2099, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.979903602783967, \"rank\": 0.020464851012057018, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The were the best guys when it really mattered.\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2167, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best guys\", \"from\": 2129, \"to\": 2142}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I want to congratulate them all on a great performance!\\\"\", \"from\": 2168, \"to\": 2228, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a great performance\", \"from\": 2207, \"to\": 2226}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking this morning, Kerr said he had yet to see the Instagram post.\", \"from\": 2230, \"to\": 2300, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2285, \"end\": 2294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4165001281198959e-27, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kerr\", \"from\": 2253, \"to\": 2257}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said: \\\"I have heard that he's said something nice.\", \"from\": 2301, \"to\": 2354, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2339, \"to\": 2348}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will believe it when I see it.\", \"from\": 2355, \"to\": 2387, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was a big race, a fast race, he took it out pretty hard yesterday which is a very brave move.\", \"from\": 2389, \"to\": 2486, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a big race\", \"from\": 2397, \"to\": 2407}, {\"ngram\": \"a fast race\", \"from\": 2409, \"to\": 2420}, {\"ngram\": \"a very brave move\", \"from\": 2468, \"to\": 2485}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think both of us got beaten by a better man.\\\"\", \"from\": 2487, \"to\": 2534, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2503, \"to\": 2505}, {\"ngram\": \"a better man\", \"from\": 2520, \"to\": 2532}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kerr revealed he had met up with family, friends and sponsors in a Parisian bar late on Tuesday night and said that in terms of a night's sleep that it had been \\\"minutes versus hours\\\".\", \"from\": 2536, \"to\": 2720, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kerr\", \"from\": 2536, \"to\": 2540}, {\"ngram\": \"family\", \"from\": 2569, \"to\": 2575}, {\"ngram\": \"friends\", \"from\": 2577, \"to\": 2584}, {\"ngram\": \"sponsors\", \"from\": 2589, \"to\": 2597}, {\"ngram\": \"a Parisian bar\", \"from\": 2601, \"to\": 2615}, {\"ngram\": \"Tuesday night\", \"from\": 2624, \"to\": 2637}, {\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 2655, \"to\": 2660}, {\"ngram\": \"a night's sleep\", \"from\": 2664, \"to\": 2679}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"minutes\", \"from\": 2697, \"to\": 2705}, {\"ngram\": \"hours\", \"from\": 2713, \"to\": 2718}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition, he wasn't feeling the freshest having had a handful of pints because his \\\"hand was full at all times\\\".\", \"from\": 2722, \"to\": 2837, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"addition\", \"from\": 2725, \"to\": 2733}, {\"ngram\": \"a handful\", \"from\": 2777, \"to\": 2786}, {\"ngram\": \"pints\", \"from\": 2790, \"to\": 2795}, {\"ngram\": \"his \\\"hand\", \"from\": 2804, \"to\": 2813}, {\"ngram\": \"all times\", \"from\": 2826, \"to\": 2835}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He added: \\\"My head's a little sore this morning but that's better than the legs being sore\\\".\", \"from\": 2838, \"to\": 2930, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My head\", \"from\": 2849, \"to\": 2856}, {\"ngram\": \"a little sore\", \"from\": 2859, \"to\": 2872}, {\"ngram\": \"the legs\", \"from\": 2909, \"to\": 2917}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kerr had looked to be on his way to gold when he passed Ingebrigtsen down the home straight only for Hocker to surprise them both up the inside to take an unexpected win in a captivating finish at theParis Olympics.\", \"from\": 2932, \"to\": 3147, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kerr\", \"from\": 2932, \"to\": 2936}, {\"ngram\": \"his way\", \"from\": 2957, \"to\": 2964}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 2968, \"to\": 2972}, {\"ngram\": \"Ingebrigtsen\", \"from\": 2988, \"to\": 3000}, {\"ngram\": \"the home\", \"from\": 3006, \"to\": 3014}, {\"ngram\": \"Hocker\", \"from\": 3033, \"to\": 3039}, {\"ngram\": \"the inside\", \"from\": 3065, \"to\": 3075}, {\"ngram\": \"an unexpected win\", \"from\": 3084, \"to\": 3101}, {\"ngram\": \"a captivating finish\", \"from\": 3105, \"to\": 3125}, {\"ngram\": \"theParis Olympics\", \"from\": 3129, \"to\": 3146}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kerr still clinched a British record come the finish, which he said was a silver lining, and admitted he was still processing how the race had played out during his media duties throughout the day.\", \"from\": 3149, \"to\": 3346, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3171, \"end\": 3185, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Progression_of_